  <!-- INTRO -->
  <div class="prose">
    <p>In January 2026, Shopify launched Agentic Storefronts as part of their Winter &apos;26 Edition &mdash; a feature that turns AI platforms like ChatGPT, Google AI Mode, Microsoft Copilot, and Perplexity into fully functioning sales channels for your store. When a customer asks ChatGPT &ldquo;what&apos;s the best running shoe for wide feet under $120?&rdquo;, your products can now appear in the response &mdash; and the customer can buy directly inside the conversation without visiting your store.</p>
    <p>This guide covers the complete setup process, including the parts most guides skip: the Knowledge Base App, product data requirements, the critical limitations that affect tracking and checkout, and a concrete action plan for stores that aren&apos;t eligible yet. The preparation matters whether you can enable it today or not &mdash; your products are already being crawled and recommended by AI platforms regardless of your settings.</p>
    <p>If you&apos;re evaluating your full Shopify stack while setting this up, it&apos;s worth noting that email marketing costs are the second-largest app expense for most stores after tracking tools. <a href="https://stackarchitect.xyz/replace-klaviyo-free">Replacing Klaviyo with Systeme.io&apos;s free plan</a> saves $150&ndash;$400/month and takes 30 minutes &mdash; the same time investment as the Knowledge Base App setup below.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="callout amber">
    <span class="callout-label">&#9888; Still in early access &mdash; US only</span>
    <p>As of March 2026, Agentic Storefronts are in early access and <strong>currently only available for US-based stores selling to US customers.</strong> International stores are not yet eligible for direct AI checkout &mdash; though your products are still discoverable by AI platforms via web crawling and Shopify Catalog. The preparation steps in this guide apply to all stores regardless of eligibility. Section 9 covers exactly what to do if you can&apos;t enable it yet.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- SECTION 1: WHAT IS -->
  <div class="sec-mark" id="what-is">01 &mdash; What Agentic Storefronts actually are</div>

  <div class="prose">
    <h2>What Are Shopify Agentic Storefronts?</h2>
    <p>Shopify Agentic Storefronts connect your product catalog to AI platforms through a single setup in your Shopify admin, allowing your products to be discovered and purchased directly inside AI conversations &mdash; with no separate integrations required for each platform.</p>
    <p>There&apos;s an important distinction most merchants miss. <strong>Product discovery on AI platforms already happens without Agentic Storefronts.</strong> AI platforms like ChatGPT and Google already crawl the web and can recommend your products. What Agentic Storefronts adds is <em>direct checkout</em> &mdash; the ability for a customer to complete a purchase inside ChatGPT without being redirected to your store.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="callout green">
    <span class="callout-label">// Discovery vs checkout &mdash; the key distinction</span>
    <p><strong>Without Agentic Storefronts active:</strong> AI platforms can recommend your products (via web crawling and Shopify Catalog), but customers are redirected to your store to complete the purchase.<br><br>
    <strong>With Agentic Storefronts active:</strong> Customers can discover your products AND complete checkout directly inside the AI conversation. Your pricing and inventory stay current in real time. Orders appear in Shopify Admin with full channel attribution.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- SECTION 2: ELIGIBILITY -->
  <div class="sec-mark" id="eligibility">02 &mdash; Eligibility requirements</div>

  <div class="prose">
    <h2>Who Is Eligible for Shopify Agentic Storefronts?</h2>
    <p>Eligibility check takes 60 seconds: go to <strong>Shopify Admin &rarr; Settings &rarr; Apps and sales channels</strong>. If you see an &ldquo;Agentic Storefronts&rdquo; section, your store is eligible. If not, review the requirements below.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="elig-grid">
    <div class="elig-card yes">
      <div class="elig-title">Required to be eligible</div>
      <ul class="elig-list">
        <li>US-based store selling to US customers</li>
        <li>Terms of Service added to your store (Settings &rarr; Policies)</li>
        <li>Privacy Policy added to your store</li>
        <li>Refund Policy added to your store</li>
        <li>Guest checkout enabled (customers cannot be required to log in)</li>
        <li>Agreement to Shopify&apos;s Agentic Storefronts Supplemental ToS</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="elig-card no">
      <div class="elig-title">Not yet supported</div>
      <ul class="elig-list">
        <li>Non-US stores (international rollout in progress)</li>
        <li>Stores requiring mandatory customer login before checkout</li>
        <li>Stores without published policies</li>
        <li>Subscription-only product catalogs</li>
        <li>Stores on Shopify Starter plan</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="vbox amber">
    <strong>Not eligible yet?</strong> Sign up at <a href="https://shopify.com/chatgpt" target="_blank" rel="noopener">shopify.com/chatgpt</a> to be notified when your store becomes eligible. Shopify is rolling out eligibility in stages through 2026. International stores are expected in H2 2026.
  </div>

