    </details>
    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>Can customers still find my products on ChatGPT if I don&apos;t enable Agentic Storefronts? <span class="faq-ico"></span></summary>
      <div class="faq-ans">
        Yes. Your products can still be discovered and recommended via web crawling and Shopify Catalog, regardless of your Agentic Storefronts settings. The difference is checkout: with Agentic Storefronts active, customers can purchase directly inside the AI chat. Without it, they are redirected to your Shopify store to complete the purchase. <strong>Discovery is automatic. Direct AI checkout requires Agentic Storefronts to be enabled.</strong>
      </div>
    </details>
    <details class="faq-item">
      <summary>What are the key limitations of Shopify Agentic Storefronts? <span class="faq-ico"></span></summary>
